                  ነአኵተከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ [በፍቁር፡ ወልድከ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡] ዘበደኃሪ፡ መዋዕል፡
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1104Anapho#Incipit">
               <t:ab>
                  Naʾakkʷǝtaka ʾǝgziʾo [ba-fǝqur waldǝka ʾǝgziʾǝna ʾIyasus] za-ba-daḫāri mawāʿǝl
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Bread">
               <t:ab>ጸሎተ፡ ፈትቶ፡ ፡ ዘቅዳሴ፡ ሐዋርያት፡</t:ab>
